chaoyang.intro.message: From Chaoyang, Beijing to Chaoyang City, Liaoning. Although the name suggests facing the sun twice, from a temporal dimension, the G3691 I took was actually heading towards the dusk. The scenery I saw was mostly brown earth and dim skies. ChaoyangÂ², perhaps it's a case of two positives making a negative.

phantasm.explanation.phantom.message: Digital photos, arranged by algorithms from storage media, disguised as holographic projections of the material world on a screen.

phantasm.explanation.ghost.message: A photo is a 'this-has-been' where the passing moment is stripped away by the shutter and lingers in a static frame.

phantasm.explanation.mental.message: Surpassing the thinness of the physical level, it builds a memory palace deep in consciousness that is more solid than reality.

modal.aspectRatio.text.message: Compared to the 3:2 of full frame, the 4:3 aspect ratio of medium format allows for framing more of the sky or the ground.

modal.focalLength.text.message: GF45mm f/2.8 is equivalent to approximately a 36mm full-frame focal length on medium format, providing a gentle perspective similar to the human eye. Neither exaggerated nor cramped, it is an ideal choice for recording the real world.

modal.ultimateTruth.text.message: 102 million pixels, combined with the excellent dynamic range and color depth of the medium format sensor, record the ultimate truthâ€”not just the visible details in the frame, but the emotional connection between reality and memory. But photos are fake after all, where is the boundary between reality and illusion? That is the question.

giclee.intro.p1.line1.message: We've always been thinking: when those magnificent world-famous paintings are dipped into the vat of fantasy and return to reality, how should they arrive by our side?

giclee.intro.p1.line2.message: As common, glare-heavy posters? Or rough-surfaced plastic sheets that curl and fade after hanging for a while?

giclee.intro.vision.message: The girls of Gensokyo deserve the highest level of treatment.

giclee.intro.p2.message: To perfectly replicate the gorgeous world under the artist's brush, we follow {standard} to create all our 'GiclÃ©e' products.

giclee.intro.p3.message: This is not just a picture, but a piece of physical collection that can be passed down.
